OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMPs call for end to sex    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Foffender name changes      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, MPs are calling on the government to   
OL,6, bring in a law to prevent sex offenders
OL,7, changing their name to avoid going on  
OL,8, the sex offenders' register.           
OL,10,FMark Fletcher, the MP for Bolsover in  
OL,11,FDerbyshire, is due to raise the issue  
OL,12,Fin a bill that will come before        
OL,13,FParliament on Wednesday.               
OL,15,FHe said he became aware of the issue   
OL,16,Fafter being contacted by a constituent.
OL,18,FThe Home Office said sex offenders must
OL,19,Fnotify police of their personal details
OL,20,Fevery year, including any name changes.
